show.description: Struggling artist Meera Sharma never imagined her path would cross with arrogant yet irresistible billionaire heir Arjun Khanna. But when a twist of fate forces her to pretend to be his fiancée, her carefully guarded secret is at risk. As a web of lies pulls them closer, Meera must choose between protecting the truth and surrendering to a love that could destroy her. Watch Now!
